WEBVTT

00:00:04.370 --> 00:00:09.369
Heinrich Dichmann and his brother August were in Saxon housing.

00:00:09.369 --> 00:00:13.369
The essays tried a new pressure tactic on the witnesses.

00:00:13.369 --> 00:00:16.370
Soon after the war broke out on September 1st,

00:00:16.370 --> 00:00:21.370
Wija Hova's witnesses had to assemble at the entrance.

00:00:21.370 --> 00:00:25.370
August Dichmann had refused to perform military service.

00:00:25.370 --> 00:00:30.370
And Baranowski, the commander whose nickname was Four Square,

00:00:30.370 --> 00:00:33.369
asked Himmler to confirm the death sentence.

00:00:33.369 --> 00:00:38.369
That came through, and the prisoners built a huge wall for the bullets.

00:00:38.369 --> 00:00:43.369
The whole camp was assembled.

00:00:43.369 --> 00:00:52.219
I just want to mention that the commander delivered a talk before the shooting.

00:00:52.219 --> 00:00:56.219
His microphone was standing about there.

00:00:56.219 --> 00:01:00.219
I can clearly remember one sentence.

00:01:00.219 --> 00:01:05.219
When he said, the prisoner August Dichmann does not regard himself

00:01:05.219 --> 00:01:12.219
a citizen of the German Reich, but rather a citizen of the Kingdom of God.

00:01:12.219 --> 00:01:17.219
Suddenly, a member of the SS came from between the barracks,

00:01:17.219 --> 00:01:23.219
with August Dichmann, and led him to the war.

00:01:23.219 --> 00:01:28.219
August was standing at the front, and we 300, about 300 brothers,

00:01:28.219 --> 00:01:34.219
with standing at the most eight or ten paces away from him.

00:01:34.219 --> 00:01:38.219
He had to stand with his face to the wall,

00:01:38.219 --> 00:01:41.219
and there were seven members of the SS.

00:01:41.219 --> 00:01:44.219
An officer with the rank of Stumbann FÃ¼hrer,

00:01:44.219 --> 00:01:55.430
that is with four stars, gave the order to shoot.

00:01:55.430 --> 00:02:00.430
When the shots were fired, he fell straight to the ground,

00:02:01.430 --> 00:02:06.430
and the SS officer drew his pistol and gave him the coup de gras.

00:02:06.430 --> 00:02:09.430
As was the custom.
